"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"legende\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:InsertMenuLegend\">Opens the <emph>Legend </emph>dialog, which allows you to change the position of legends in the chart, and to specify whether the legend is displayed.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"legende\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:InsertMenuLegend\">ເປີດກ່ອງສົນທະນາ <emph>ຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກ </emph>, ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານປ່ຽນຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກໃນແຜນພູມ, ແລະ ລະບຸວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງຜົນຫຼືບໍ່.</ahelp></variable>"

