"par_id3154684\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"besch\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:InsertMenuDataLabels\">Opens the<emph> Data Labels </emph>dialog, which enables you to set the data labels.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"besch\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:InsertMenuDataLabels\">ເປີດກ່ອງສົນທະນາ<emph> ປ້າຍຊື່ຂໍ້ມູນ </emph>, ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຕັ້ງຄ່າປ້າຍຊື່ຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້.</ahelp></variable>"

#. EwAhi
