"par_id9078573\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id9078573\" src=\"chart2/res/step_start_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id9078573\">Start step icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id9078573\" src=\"chart2/res/step_start_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id9078573\">ໄອຄອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂັ້ນ</alt></image>"

#. q9CgC
#: stepped_line_properties.xhp
msgctxt ""
"stepped_line_properties.xhp\n"
"par_id9047365\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Start with horizontal line and step up vertically at the end."
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍເສັ້ນແນວນອນ ແລະ ຂຶ້ນເປັນຂັ້ນໄດແນວຕັ້ງຢູ່ຕອນທ້າຍ."

#. n5BBu
#: stepped_line_properties.xhp
msgctxt ""
"stepped_line_properties.xhp\n"
"par_id05495673\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id05495673\" src=\"chart2/res/step_end_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id05495673\">End step icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id05495673\" src=\"chart2/res/step_end_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id05495673\">ໄອຄອນສິ້ນສຸດຂັ້ນ</alt></image>"

#. 8FtSp
#: stepped_line_properties.xhp
msgctxt ""
"stepped_line_properties.xhp\n"
"par_id439028\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Start to step up vertically and end with horizontal line."
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍການຂຶ້ນເປັນຂັ້ນໄດແນວຕັ້ງ ແລະ ສິ້ນສຸດດ້ວຍເສັ້ນແນວນອນ."

#. CYGwd
#: stepped_line_properties.xhp
msgctxt ""
"stepped_line_properties.xhp\n"
"par_id9673426\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id9673426\" src=\"chart2/res/step_center_x_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id9673426\">Center X icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id9673426\" src=\"chart2/res/step_center_x_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id9673426\">ໄອຄອນກາງ X</alt></image>"

#. 5HiqU
#: stepped_line_properties.xhp
msgctxt ""
"stepped_line_properties.xhp\n"
"par_id4069483\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Start with horizontal line, step up vertically in the middle of the X values and end with horizontal line."
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍເສັ້ນແນວນອນ, ຂຶ້ນເປັນຂັ້ນໄດແນວຕັ້ງຢູ່ເຄິ່ງກາງຂອງຄ່າ X ແລະ ສິ້ນສຸດດ້ວຍເສັ້ນແນວນອນ."

#. izGd7
#: stepped_line_properties.xhp
msgctxt ""
"stepped_line_properties.xhp\n"
"par_id56635427\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id56635427\" src=\"chart2/res/step_center_y_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id56635427\">Center Y icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id56635427\" src=\"chart2/res/step_center_y_30.svg\" width=\"30px\" height=\"30px\"><alt id=\"alt_id56635427\">ໄອຄອນກາງ Y</alt></image>"

#. aSX46
#: stepped_line_properties.xhp
msgctxt ""
"stepped_line_properties.xhp\n"
"par_id0679473\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Start to step up vertically to the middle of the Y values, draw a horizontal line and finish by stepping vertically to the end."
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍການຂຶ້ນເປັນຂັ້ນໄດແນວຕັ້ງໄປຫາເຄິ່ງກາງຂອງຄ່າ Y, ແຕ້ມເສັ້ນແນວນອນ ແລະ ສິ້ນສຸດໂດຍການຂຶ້ນເປັນຂັ້ນໄດແນວຕັ້ງໄປຫາຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດ."

#. FvgkA
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "3D View"
msgstr "ມຸມເບິ່ງ 3 ມິຕິ"

#. MPJ28
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"bm_id3156423\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>3D charts</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>charts; 3D views</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>illumination; 3D charts</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ແຜນພູມ 3 ມິຕິ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ແຜນພູມ; ມຸມເບິ່ງ 3 ມິຕິ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການສ່ອງແສງ; ແຜນພູມ 3 ມິຕິ</bookmark_value>"

#. D5fGV
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"hd_id3464461\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"three_d_view\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/three_d_view.xhp\">3D View</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"three_d_view\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/three_d_view.xhp\">ມຸມເບິ່ງ 3 ມິຕິ</link></variable>"

#. K3TFE
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id6998809\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the first page of the <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">Chart Wizard</link> or in the context menu of a chart you can choose a chart type. <ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Opens a dialog to edit the properties of a three dimensional view for Column, Bar, Pie, and Area charts. For Line and XY (Scatter) charts you can see 3D lines.</ahelp>"
msgstr "ໃນໜ້າທຳອິດຂອງ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</link> ຫຼື ໃນເມນູຄລິກຂວາຂອງແຜນພູມ ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກປະເພດແຜນພູມໄດ້. <ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເປີດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງມຸມເບິ່ງສາມມິຕິສຳລັບແຜນພູມແທ່ງຕັ້ງ, ແທ່ງນອນ, ວົງມົນ ແລະ ພື້ນທີ່. ສຳລັບແຜນພູມເສັ້ນ ແລະ ແຜນພູມ XY (ກະຈາຍ) ເຈົ້າສາມາດເຫັນເປັນເສັ້ນ 3 ມິຕິໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. FJdFw
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id6942045\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The chart preview responds to the new settings that you enter in the dialog."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງແຜນພູມຈະສະແດງຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃໝ່ທີ່ເຈົ້າປ້ອນເຂົ້າໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ."

#. ECHVW
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3806878\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you leave the dialog with OK, the settings are applied permanently."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເຈົ້າປິດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມດ້ວຍການກົດ ຕົກລົງ (OK), ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ຢ່າງຖາວອນ."

#. MGhrT
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id130619\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you leave the dialog with Cancel or Escape, the chart returns to the state when you opened the dialog."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເຈົ້າປິດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມດ້ວຍການກົດ ຍົກເລີກ (Cancel) ຫຼື ປຸ່ມ Escape, ແຜນພູມຈະກັບຄືນສູ່ສະພາວະກ່ອນທີ່ເຈົ້າຈະເປີດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ."

#. 6fpbE
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id8081911\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For a 3D chart you can choose <item type=\"menuitem\">Format - 3D View</item> to set perspective, appearance and illumination."
msgstr "ສຳລັບແຜນພູມ 3 ມິຕິ ເເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຮູບແບບ - ມຸມເບິ່ງ 3 ມິຕິ</item> ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າທັດສະນະມິຕິ (perspective), ຮູບລັກສະນະ ແລະ ການສ່ອງແສງ."

#. kB3EJ
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"hd_id2924283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Perspective"
msgstr "ທັດສະນະມິຕິ"

#. uEsKT
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id5781731\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the values for rotation of the chart on the three axes and for a perspective view."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຄ່າສຳລັບການໝູນແຜນພູມໃນສາມແກນ ແລະ ສຳລັບມຸມເບິ່ງທັດສະນະມິຕິ."

#. q86vQ
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id9999694\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set all angles to 0 for a front view of the chart. Pie charts and donut charts are shown as circles."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າທຸກມຸມເປັນ 0 ສຳລັບມຸມເບິ່ງດ້ານໜ້າຂອງແຜນພູມ. ແຜນພູມວົງມົນ ແລະ ແຜນພູມໂດນັດຈະສະແດງເປັນຮູບວົງມົນ."

#. 7gq8D
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id2861720\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With Right-angled axes enabled, you can rotate the chart contents only in X and Y direction, that is, parallel to the chart borders."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານ ແກນມຸມສາກ (Right-angled axes), ເຈົ້າສາມາດໝູນເນື້ອໃນແຜນພູມໄດ້ສະເພາະໃນທິດທາງ X ແລະ Y ເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ນັ້ນຄື ຈະຂະໜານກັບຂອບຂອງແຜນພູມ."

#. WbNFp
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id2216559\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An x value of 90, with y and z set to 0, provides a view from top down to the chart. With x set to -90, you see the bottom of the chart."
msgstr "ຄ່າ x ເປັນ 90, ໂດຍຕັ້ງຄ່າ y ແລະ z ເປັນ 0, ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເຫັນມຸມເບິ່ງຈາກເທິງລົງລຸ່ມ. ຖ້າຕັ້ງຄ່າ x ເປັນ -90, ເຈົ້າຈະເຫັນດ້ານລຸ່ມຂອງແຜນພູມ."

#. x4gAP
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id7869502\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The rotations are applied in the order first x, then y, last z."
msgstr "ການໝູນຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ຕາມລຳດັບຄື: x ກ່ອນ, ຈາກນັ້ນແມ່ນ y, ແລະ ສຸດທ້າຍແມ່ນ z."

#. dJrGA
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id9852900\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When shading is enabled and you rotate a chart, the lights are rotated as if they are fixed to the chart."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານການເຮັດເງົາ (shading) ແລະ ເຈົ້າໝູນແຜນພູມ, ແສງໄຟຈະໝູນໄປນຳຄືກັບວ່າມັນຖືກຍຶດຕິດໄວ້ກັບແຜນພູມ."

#. dkHpm
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id2578203\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The rotation axes always relate to the page, not to the chart's axes. This is different from some other chart programs."
msgstr "ແກນການໝູນຈະກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບໜ້າເຈ້ຍສະເໝີ, ບໍ່ແມ່ນກ່ຽວກັບແກນຂອງແຜນພູມ. ສິ່ງນີ້ແຕກຕ່າງຈາກໂປຣແກຣມແຜນພູມອື່ນໆບາງໂປຣແກຣມ."

#. TCAhS
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id4923245\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the Perspective check box to view the chart in central perspective as through a camera lens instead of using a parallel projection."
msgstr "ໝາຍເລືອກຊ່ອງ ທັດສະນະມິຕິ (Perspective) ເພື່ອເບິ່ງແຜນພູມໃນຮູບແບບທັດສະນະມິຕິຄືກັບເບິ່ງຜ່ານເລນກ້ອງຖ່າຍຮູບ ແທນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ການສາຍພາບແບບຂະໜານ."

#. ttWsp
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3416547\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the focus length with the spin button. 100% gives a perspective view where a far edge in the chart looks approximately half as big as a near edge."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມຍາວໂຟກັດດ້ວຍປຸ່ມປັບຄ່າ. 100% ຈະໃຫ້ມຸມເບິ່ງທັດສະນະມິຕິທີ່ຂອບດ້ານໄກຂອງແຜນພູມຈະເບິ່ງຄືວ່າມີຂະໜາດນ້ອຍກວ່າຂອບດ້ານໃກ້ປະມານເຄິ່ງໜຶ່ງ."

#. X7UoV
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3791924\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Older versions of %PRODUCTNAME cannot display the percentage of perspective the same way as the current version."
msgstr "ເວີຊັນເກົ່າຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME ບໍ່ສາມາດສະແດງເປີເຊັນຂອງທັດສະນະມິຕິໃນຮູບແບບດຽວກັນກັບເວີຊັນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. SY4DN
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id7623828\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">If Right-angled axes is enabled, you can rotate the chart contents only in X and Y direction, that is, parallel to the chart borders. Right-angled axes is enabled by default for newly created 3D charts. Pie and Donut charts do not support right-angled axes.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຫາກເປີດໃຊ້ງານ ແກນມຸມສາກ, ເຈົ້າສາມາດໝູນເນື້ອໃນແຜນພູມໄດ້ສະເພາະໃນທິດທາງ X ແລະ Y ເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ນັ້ນຄື ຂະໜານກັບຂອບແຜນພູມ. ແກນມຸມສາກຈະຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສຳລັບແຜນພູມ 3 ມິຕິທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃໝ່. ແຜນພູມວົງມົນ ແລະ ແຜນພູມໂດນັດບໍ່ຮອງຮັບແກນມຸມສາກ.</ahelp>"

#. AWYCE
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id4721823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Sets the rotation of the chart on the x axis. The preview responds to the new settings.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າການໝູນແຜນພູມໃນແກນ x. ຕົວຢ່າງຈະສະແດງຜົນຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃໝ່.</ahelp>"

#. r68Bu
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id5806756\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Sets the rotation of the chart on the y axis. The preview responds to the new settings.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າການໝູນແຜນພູມໃນແກນ y. ຕົວຢ່າງຈະສະແດງຜົນຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃໝ່.</ahelp>"

#. HG7NF
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id8915372\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Sets the rotation of the chart on the z axis. The preview responds to the new settings.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າການໝູນແຜນພູມໃນແກນ z. ຕົວຢ່າງຈະສະແດງຜົນຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃໝ່.</ahelp>"

#. P3E59
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id6070436\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Mark the Perspective box to view the chart as through a camera lens. Use the spin button to set the percentage. With a high percentage nearer objects look bigger than more distant objects.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ໝາຍເລືອກຊ່ອງ ທັດສະນະມິຕິ ເພື່ອເບິ່ງແຜນພູມຄືກັບຜ່ານເລນກ້ອງ. ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມປັບຄ່າເພື່ອຕັ້ງເປີເຊັນ. ເມື່ອມີເປີເຊັນສູງ ວັດຖຸທີ່ຢູ່ໃກ້ຈະເບິ່ງໃຫຍ່ກວ່າວັດຖຸທີ່ຢູ່ໄກ.</ahelp>"

#. PYRAg
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"hd_id7564012\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "ຮູບລັກສະນະ"

#. ExGom
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id1186254\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select a scheme from the list box."
msgstr "ເລືອກຮູບແບບ (scheme) ຈາກກ່ອງລາຍການ."

#. NyTEB
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id7432477\n"
"help.text"
msgid "By selecting a scheme, the check boxes and the light sources are set accordingly."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເລືອກຮູບແບບໃດໜຶ່ງ, ຊ່ອງໝາຍເລືອກ ແລະ ແຫຼ່ງກຳເນີດແສງຈະຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າຕາມນັ້ນ."

#. UaDvh
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id7141026\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you mark or unmark a combination of check boxes that is not given by the Realistic or Simple scheme, you create a Custom scheme."
msgstr "ຫາກເຈົ້າໝາຍເລືອກ ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍໃນຮູບແບບທີ່ບໍ່ມີໃນແບບ ສົມຈິງ (Realistic) ຫຼື ແບບ ງ່າຍດາຍ (Simple), ເຈົ້າຈະສ້າງເປັນແບບ ກຳນົດເອງ (Custom)."

#. A6j2j
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id1579027\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Mark <emph>Shading</emph> to use the Gouraud method for rendering the surface, otherwise a flat method is used."
msgstr "ໝາຍເລືອກ <emph>ການເຮັດເງົາ</emph> ເພື່ອໃຊ້ວິທີ Gouraud ສຳລັບການສະແດງຜົນພື້ນຜິວ, ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນຈະໃຊ້ວິທີແບບຮາບພຽງ (flat)."

#. WRqk7
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id5624561\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The flat method sets a single color and brightness for each polygon. The edges are visible, soft gradients and spot lights are not possible."
msgstr "ວິທີແບບຮາບພຽງຈະຕັ້ງຄ່າສີ ແລະ ຄວາມສະຫວ່າງດຽວໃຫ້ກັບແຕ່ລະຮູບຫຼາຍຫຼ່ຽມ. ຈະເຫັນຂອບໄດ້ຊັດເຈນ, ບໍ່ສາມາດເຮັດການໄລ່ສີແບບນຸ້ມນວນ ຫຼື ໄຟສ່ອງສະເພາະຈຸດໄດ້."

#. DnfGG
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id5901058\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Gouraud method applies gradients for a smoother, more realistic look."
msgstr "ວິທີ Gouraud ຈະໃຊ້ການໄລ່ສີເພື່ອໃຫ້ເບິ່ງລຽບນຽນ ແລະ ສົມຈິງຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. AAcgf
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id8469191\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Mark <emph>Object Borders</emph> to draw lines along the edges."
msgstr "ໝາຍເລືອກ <emph>ຂອບວັດຖຸ</emph> ເພື່ອແຕ້ມເສັ້ນຕາມຂອບຕ່າງໆ."

#. pjkcz
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id4407483\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Mark <emph>Rounded Edges</emph> to smooth the edges of box shapes."
msgstr "ໝາຍເລືອກ <emph>ຂອບມົນ</emph> ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ຂອບຂອງຮູບຊົງກ່ອງມີຄວາມມົນລຽບ."

#. 5nhwU
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id8531449\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Select a scheme from the list box, or click any of the check boxes below.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລືອກຮູບແບບຈາກກ່ອງລາຍການ, ຫຼື ຄລິກທີ່ຊ່ອງໝາຍເລືອກໃດໜຶ່ງຂ້າງລຸ່ມ.</ahelp>"

#. anDsd
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id9183935\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Applies Gouraud shading if marked, or flat shading if unmarked.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ນຳໃຊ້ການເຮັດເງົາແບບ Gouraud ຫາກໝາຍເລືອກ, ຫຼື ການເຮັດເງົາແບບຮາບພຽງຫາກບໍ່ໝາຍເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. uFdmA
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id946684\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Shows borders around the areas by setting the line style to Solid.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ສະແດງຂອບອ້ອມຮອບພື້ນທີ່ໂດຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າຮູບແບບເສັ້ນເປັນເສັ້ນທຶບ (Solid).</ahelp>"

#. fdS3G
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id9607226\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Edges are rounded by 5%.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຂອບຈະຖືກເຮັດໃຫ້ມົນ 5%.</ahelp>"

#. Z5qYF
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"hd_id1939451\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Illumination"
msgstr "ການສ່ອງແສງ"

#. wxTjk
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id9038972\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Set the light sources for the 3D view.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າແຫຼ່ງກຳເນີດແສງສຳລັບມຸມເບິ່ງ 3 ມິຕິ.</ahelp>"

#. Bs7GH
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id6531266\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click any of the eight buttons to switch a directed light source on or off."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ປຸ່ມໃດໜຶ່ງໃນແປດປຸ່ມເພື່ອເປີດ ຫຼື ປິດແຫຼ່ງກຳເນີດແສງທີ່ກຳນົດທິດທາງ."

#. FbkLw
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id6173894\n"
"help.text"
msgid "By default, the second light source is switched on. It is the first of seven \"normal\", uniform light sources. The light source number one projects a specular light with highlights."
msgstr "ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ແຫຼ່ງກຳເນີດແສງທີສອງຈະຖືກເປີດໄວ້. ມັນແມ່ນອັນທຳອິດຂອງແຫຼ່ງແສງ \"ປົກກະຕິ\" ເຈັດອັນທີ່ມີຄວາມສະຫວ່າງສະໝໍ່າສະເໝີ. ແຫຼ່ງແສງໝາຍເລກໜຶ່ງຈະສ່ອງແສງແບບສະທ້ອນ (specular) ທີ່ມີຈຸດເດັ່ນຂອງແສງ."

#. yrBh7
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id2761314\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For the selected light source, you can then choose a color and intensity in the list box just below the eight buttons. The brightness values of all lights are added, so use dark colors when you enable multiple lights."
msgstr "ສຳລັບແຫຼ່ງແສງທີ່ເລືອກ, ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກສີ ແລະ ຄວາມເຂັ້ມຂຸ້ນໄດ້ໃນກ່ອງລາຍການທີ່ຢູ່ລຸ່ມແປດປຸ່ມນັ້ນ. ຄ່າຄວາມສະຫວ່າງຂອງແສງທັງໝົດຈະຖືກລວມເຂົ້າກັນ, ສະນັ້ນຄວນໃຊ້ສີເຂັ້ມເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ໄຟຫຼາຍດວງ."

#. 2XSXK
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3912778\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The small preview inside this tab page has two sliders to set the vertical and horizontal position of the selected light source. The light source always aims to the middle of the object."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງຂະໜາດນ້ອຍພາຍໃນແຖບນີ້ມີຕົວເລື່ອນສອງອັນເພື່ອຕັ້ງຕຳແໜ່ງແນວຕັ້ງ ແລະ ແນວນອນຂອງແຫຼ່ງແສງທີ່ເລືອກ. ແຫຼ່ງແສງຈະສ່ອງໄປຫາຈຸດເຄິ່ງກາງຂອງວັດຖຸສະເໝີ."

#. GCEnz
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3163853\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The button in the corner of the small preview switches the internal illumination model between a sphere and a cube."
msgstr "ປຸ່ມຢູ່ມຸມຂອງຕົວຢ່າງຂະໜາດນ້ອຍຈະສະຫຼັບຕົວແບບການສ່ອງແສງພາຍໃນລະຫວ່າງຮູບຊົງມົນ ແລະ ຮູບກ້ອນສາກ."

#. zGKUA
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id121158\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the Ambient light list box to define the ambient light which shines with a uniform intensity from all directions."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ກ່ອງລາຍການ ແສງສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ (Ambient light) ເພື່ອກຳນົດແສງສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ສ່ອງສະຫວ່າງດ້ວຍຄວາມເຂັ້ມສະໝໍ່າສະເໝີຈາກທຸກທິດທາງ."

#. Eqkxr
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id2423780\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Drag the right slider to set the vertical height and direction of the selected light source.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລື່ອນຕົວເລື່ອນດ້ານຂວາເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄວາມສູງແນວຕັ້ງ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງແຫຼ່ງແສງທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. ZWk38
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id2569658\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Drag the bottom slider to set the horizontal position and direction of the selected light source.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລື່ອນຕົວເລື່ອນດ້ານລຸ່ມເພື່ອຕັ້ງຕຳແໜ່ງແນວນອນ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງແຫຼ່ງແສງທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. VmhCQ
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id6394238\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Click to switch between an illumination model of a sphere or a cube.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຄລິກເພື່ອສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງຕົວແບບການສ່ອງແສງຂອງຮູບຊົງມົນ ຫຼື ຮູບກ້ອນສາກ.</ahelp>"

#. 9ut8k
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id533768\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Click to enable or disable the specular light source with highlights.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຄລິກເພື່ອເປີດ ຫຼື ປິດແຫຼ່ງກຳເນີດແສງແບບສະທ້ອນທີ່ມີຈຸດເດັ່ນ.</ahelp>"

#. muQW4
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id7214270\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Click to enable or disable the uniform light source.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຄລິກເພື່ອເປີດ ຫຼື ປິດແຫຼ່ງກຳເນີດແສງທີ່ມີຄວາມສະຫວ່າງສະໝໍ່າສະເໝີ.</ahelp>"

#. acKKh
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id2186346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Select a color for the selected light source.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລືອກສີສຳລັບແຫຼ່ງກຳເນີດແສງທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. f2CNq
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id1331217\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Select a color using the Pick a Color dialog.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລືອກສີໂດຍໃຊ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ ເລືອກສີ.</ahelp>"

#. CkjT6
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id393993\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Select a color for the ambient light.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລືອກສີສຳລັບແສງສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ.</ahelp>"

#. eEeFt
#: three_d_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"three_d_view.xhp\n"
"par_id5871761\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Select a color using the Pick a Color dialog.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລືອກສີໂດຍໃຊ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ ເລືອກສີ.</ahelp>"

#. TzVRx
#: type_area.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_area.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Chart Type Area"
msgstr "ແຜນພູມປະເພດພື້ນທີ່"

#. AczQp
#: type_area.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_area.xhp\n"
"bm_id4130680\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>area charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>chart types;area</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ແຜນພູມພື້ນທີ່</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ປະເພດແຜນພູມ; ພື້ນທີ່</bookmark_value>"

#. 3LDy2
#: type_area.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_area.xhp\n"
"hd_id310678\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"type_area\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/type_area.xhp\">Chart Type Area</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"type_area\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/type_area.xhp\">ແຜນພູມປະເພດພື້ນທີ່</link></variable>"

#. DnkqL
#: type_area.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_area.xhp\n"
"par_id916776\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the first page of the <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">Chart Wizard</link> you can choose a chart type."
msgstr "ໃນໜ້າທຳອິດຂອງ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</link> ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກປະເພດແຜນພູມໄດ້."

#. cRPs4
#: type_area.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_area.xhp\n"
"par_id791747395583502\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Then choose <emph>Area</emph>."
msgstr "ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກ <emph>ພື້ນທີ່</emph>."

#. AXGaZ
#: type_area.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_area.xhp\n"
"hd_id961943\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Area"
msgstr "ພື້ນທີ່"

#. FKucv
#: type_area.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_area.xhp\n"
"par_id631733\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An area chart shows values as points on the y axis. The x axis shows categories. The y values of each data series are connected by a line. The area between each two lines is filled with a color. The area chart's focus is to emphasize the changes from one category to the next."
msgstr "ແຜນພູມພື້ນທີ່ສະແດງຄ່າເປັນຈຸດໃນແກນ y. ແກນ x ສະແດງປະເພດຕ່າງໆ. ຄ່າ y ຂອງແຕ່ລະຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນຖືກເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ດ້ວຍເສັ້ນ. ພື້ນທີ່ລະຫວ່າງສອງເສັ້ນຖືກເຕີມດ້ວຍສີ. ຈຸດປະສົງຂອງແຜນພູມພື້ນທີ່ແມ່ນເພື່ອເນັ້ນໜັກເຖິງການປ່ຽນແປງຈາກປະເພດໜຶ່ງໄປຫາປະເພດຖັດໄປ."

#. pt8T2
