"hd_id791747253269626\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Percent Stacked"
msgstr "ແບບຊ້ອນກັນເປັນເປີເຊັນ"

#. Fih8H
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"par_id6968901\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This subtype shows the relative percentage of each data value with regard to the total of its category. Main focus is the relative contribution of each value to the category's total."
msgstr "ປະເພດຍ່ອຍນີ້ສະແດງເປີເຊັນສຳພັດຂອງແຕ່ລະຄ່າຂໍ້ມູນເມື່ອທຽບກັບຄ່າລວມຂອງປະເພດນັ້ນ. ຈຸດປະສົງຫຼັກແມ່ນເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຫັນສັດສ່ວນຂອງແຕ່ລະຄ່າຕໍ່ຄ່າລວມທັງໝົດຂອງປະເພດ."

#. BxWk3
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"par_id731747253502324\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"chart2/res/columnpercent_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id851747253502326\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id251747253502329\">Icon Percent Stacked</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"chart2/res/columnpercent_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id851747253502326\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id251747253502329\">ໄອຄອນ ແບບຊ້ອນກັນເປັນເປີເຊັນ</alt></image>"

#. EwFwi
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"par_id91747253502334\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Percent Stacked"
msgstr "ແບບຊ້ອນກັນເປັນເປີເຊັນ"

#. ebC4P
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"hd_id381747253313672\n"
"help.text"
msgid "3D View"
msgstr "ມຸມເບິ່ງ 3 ມິຕິ"

#. XEMVB
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"par_id2224494\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can enable a <link href=\"text/schart/01/three_d_view.xhp\">3D view</link> of the data values. The \"realistic\" scheme tries to give the best 3D look. The \"simple\" scheme tries to mimic the chart view of other Office products."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດເປີດໃຊ້ງານ <link href=\"text/schart/01/three_d_view.xhp\">ມຸມເບິ່ງ 3 ມິຕິ</link> ຂອງຄ່າຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້. ຮູບແບບ \"ສົມຈິງ\" ຈະພະຍາຍາມໃຫ້ຮູບລັກສະນະ 3 ມິຕິທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດ. ຮູບແບບ \"ງ່າຍດາຍ\" ຈະພະຍາຍາມຮຽນແບບມຸມເບິ່ງແຜນພູມຂອງຜະລິດຕະພັນ Office ອື່ນໆ."

#. KLGK5
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"par_id7359233\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For 3D charts, you can select the shape of each data value from Box, Cylinder, Cone, and Pyramid."
msgstr "ສຳລັບແຜນພູມ 3 ມິຕິ, ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກຮູບຊົງຂອງແຕ່ລະຄ່າຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້ຈາກ ຮູບກ່ອງ, ຮູບທໍ່ກົມ, ຮູບຈວຍ, ແລະ ຮູບປີຣາມິດ."

#. EhVP5
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"hd_id955839\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Bar"
msgstr "ແທ່ງນອນ"

#. DiCDp
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"par_id6596881\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This type shows a bar chart or bar graph with horizontal bars. The length of each bar is proportional to its value. The y axis shows categories. The x axis shows the value for each category."
msgstr "ປະເພດນີ້ສະແດງແຜນພູມແທ່ງ ຫຼື ກຣາບແທ່ງທີ່ມີແທ່ງໃນແນວນອນ. ຄວາມຍາວຂອງແຕ່ລະແທ່ງຈະເປັນສັດສ່ວນກັບຄ່າຂອງມັນ. ແກນ y ສະແດງປະເພດຕ່າງໆ. ແກນ x ສະແດງຄ່າສຳລັບແຕ່ລະປະເພດ."

#. uCR7E
#: type_column_bar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_bar.xhp\n"
"par_id8750572\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The subtypes are the same as for the Column type."
msgstr "ປະເພດຍ່ອຍແມ່ນຄືກັນກັບແຜນພູມປະເພດແທ່ງຕັ້ງ."

#. ShEAK
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Chart Type Column and Line"
msgstr "ແຜນພູມປະເພດແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ"

#. 3UEjb
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"bm_id5976744\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>column and line charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>chart types;column and line</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>combination charts</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ແຜນພູມແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ປະເພດແຜນພູມ; ແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ແຜນພູມແບບປະສົມ</bookmark_value>"

#. YB3oh
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"hd_id8596453\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"type_column_line\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/type_column_line.xhp\">Chart Type Column and Line</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"type_column_line\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/type_column_line.xhp\">ແຜນພູມປະເພດແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ</link></variable>"

#. djyQA
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id4818567\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the first page of the <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">Chart Wizard</link> you can choose a chart type."
msgstr "ໃນໜ້າທຳອິດຂອງ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</link> ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກປະເພດແຜນພູມໄດ້."

#. RWstF
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id791747395583502\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Then choose <emph>Column and Line</emph>."
msgstr "ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກ <emph>ແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ</emph>."

#. p8vzY
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"hd_id2451551\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Column and Line"
msgstr "ແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ"

#. WRAdR
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id3101901\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A Column and Line chart is a combination of a <link href=\"text/schart/01/type_column_bar.xhp\">Column chart</link> with a <link href=\"text/schart/01/type_line.xhp\">Line chart</link>."
msgstr "ແຜນພູມແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ ແມ່ນການປະສົມກັນລະຫວ່າງ <link href=\"text/schart/01/type_column_bar.xhp\">ແຜນພູມແທ່ງຕັ້ງ</link> ແລະ <link href=\"text/schart/01/type_line.xhp\">ແຜນພູມເສັ້ນ</link>."

#. D5YZG
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"hd_id81747397775672\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Columns and Lines"
msgstr "ແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ"

#. DuRCn
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id5244300\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The rectangles of the column data series are drawn side by side so that you can easily compare their values."
msgstr "ຮູບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນແທ່ງຕັ້ງຈະຖືກແຕ້ມໄວ້ຂ້າງກັນເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຈົ້າສາມາດປຽບທຽບຄ່າຂອງພວກມັນໄດ້ງ່າຍ."

#. pBhu7
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id831747397797160\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"chart2/res/columnline_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id161747397797163\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id471747397797165\">Icon Columns and Lines</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"chart2/res/columnline_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id161747397797163\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id471747397797165\">ໄອຄອນ ແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ</alt></image>"

#. cCfEE
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id861747397797169\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Columns and Lines"
msgstr "ແທ່ງຕັ້ງ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ"

#. ptCvG
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"hd_id441747397937219\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Stacked Columns and Lines"
msgstr "ແທ່ງຕັ້ງຊ້ອນກັນ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ"

#. 32VcG
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id7163609\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The rectangles of the column data series are drawn stacked above each other, so that the height of a column visualizes the sum of the data values."
msgstr "ຮູບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນແທ່ງຕັ້ງຈະຖືກແຕ້ມຊ້ອນກັນ, ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຄວາມສູງຂອງແທ່ງສະແດງຜົນລວມຂອງຄ່າຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. kGyvh
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id191747397961284\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"chart2/res/columnstackline_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id431747397961286\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id961747397961289\">Icon Stacked Columns and Lines</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"chart2/res/columnstackline_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id431747397961286\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id961747397961289\">ໄອຄອນ ແທ່ງຕັ້ງຊ້ອນກັນ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ</alt></image>"

#. 3sgiT
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id681747397961294\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Stacked Columns and Lines"
msgstr "ແທ່ງຕັ້ງຊ້ອນກັນ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ"

#. CGACB
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id1842097\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can insert a second y-axis with <link href=\"text/schart/01/04040000.xhp\">Insert - Axes</link> after you finish the wizard."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດແຊກແກນ y ທີສອງໄດ້ດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ <link href=\"text/schart/01/04040000.xhp\">ແຊກ - ແກນ</link> ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ເຈົ້າສຳເລັດການໃຊ້ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງ."

#. F4KnA
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"hd_id8297677\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To specify a data range"
msgstr "ການກຳນົດຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. o6dS4
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id8871120\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The leftmost columns (or the top rows) of the selected data range provide the data that are shown as Columns objects. The other columns or rows of the data range provide the data for the Lines objects. You can change this assignment in the <emph>Data Series</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ຖັນຊ້າຍສຸດ (ຫຼື ແຖວເທິງສຸດ) ຂອງຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເລືອກຈະເປັນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ສະແດງເປັນວັດຖຸແທ່ງຕັ້ງ. ຖັນ ຫຼື ແຖວອື່ນໆຂອງຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນຈະເປັນຂໍ້ມູນສຳລັບວັດຖຸເສັ້ນ. ເຈົ້າສາມາດປ່ຽນການກຳນົດນີ້ໄດ້ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>."

#. dMYwd
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id2952055\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the data range."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. CjHGL
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id594500\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click one of the options for data series in rows or in columns."
msgstr "ຄລິກເລືອກຕົວເລືອກໃດໜຶ່ງສຳລັບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນໃນແຖວ ຫຼື ໃນຖັນ."

#. JB5Ue
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id1944944\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Check whether the data range has labels in the first row or in the first column or both."
msgstr "ກວດສອບວ່າຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນມີປ້າຍຊື່ໃນແຖວທຳອິດ ຫຼື ໃນຖັນທຳອິດ ຫຼື ທັງສອງຢ່າງ."

#. sPWZN
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"hd_id6667683\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Organizing data series"
msgstr "ການຈັດລະບຽບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. Lwtzk
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id7616809\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the Data Series list box you see a list of all data series in the current chart."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງລາຍການຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ ເຈົ້າຈະເຫັນລາຍຊື່ຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດໃນແຜນພູມປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. dqMFF
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id9770195\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The column data series are positioned at the top of the list, the line data series at the bottom of the list."
msgstr "ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນແທ່ງຕັ້ງຈະຢູ່ສ່ວນເທິງຂອງລາຍການ, ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນເສັ້ນຈະຢູ່ສ່ວນລຸ່ມຂອງລາຍການ."

#. YLeMA
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id1446272\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To organize the data series, select an entry in the list."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຈັດລະບຽບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກລາຍການໃດໜຶ່ງໃນລາຍຊື່."

#. tpRFy
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id3779717\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click Add to add another data series below the selected entry. The new data series has the same type as the selected entry."
msgstr "ຄລິກ ເພີ່ມ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນອື່ນຢູ່ລຸ່ມລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກ. ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່ຈະມີປະເພດດຽວກັນກັບລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. CJAQb
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id5056611\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click Remove to remove the selected entry from the Data Series list."
msgstr "ຄລິກ ລຶບອອກ ເພື່ອລຶບລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກອອກຈາກລາຍຊື່ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. A3Fro
#: type_column_line.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_column_line.xhp\n"
"par_id7786492\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the Up and Down arrow buttons to move the selected entry in the list up or down. This way you can convert a Column data series to a List data series and back. This does not change the order in the data source table, but changes only the arrangement in the chart."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລູກສອນ ຂຶ້ນ ແລະ ລົງ ເພື່ອຍ້າຍລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກໃນລາຍຊື່ຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງ. ວິທີນີ້ເຈົ້າສາມາດປ່ຽນຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນແທ່ງຕັ້ງເປັນຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນເສັ້ນ ແລະ ປ່ຽນກັບຄືນໄດ້. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະບໍ່ປ່ຽນລຳດັບໃນຕາຕະລາງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ, ແຕ່ຈະປ່ຽນແຕ່ການຈັດລຽງໃນແຜນພູມເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. RsSsd
