msgid "<image src=\"chart2/res/stock_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id801747393380186\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id761747393380189\">Icon Stock Chart Type 1</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"chart2/res/stock_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id801747393380186\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id761747393380189\">ໄອຄອນ ແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນ ແບບທີ 1</alt></image>"

#. D9kCn
