"hd_id2318796\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Setting the Data Source"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. CoEsB
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"hd_id399182\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Charts based on its own data"
msgstr "ແຜນພູມທີ່ອີງຕາມຂໍ້ມູນຂອງມັນເອງ"

#. g5esU
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id5298318\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change the data series of a chart having its own data, choose <link href=\"text/schart/01/03010000.xhp\"><emph>Chart Data Table</emph></link> from the <emph>View</emph> menu or from the context menu of the chart in edit mode."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນຂອງແຜນພູມທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນຂອງມັນເອງ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <link href=\"text/schart/01/03010000.xhp\"><emph>ຕາຕະລາງຂໍ້ມູນແຜນພູມ</emph></link> ຈາກເມນູ <emph>ມຸມເບິ່ງ</emph> ຫຼື ຈາກເມນູຄລິກຂວາຂອງແຜນພູມໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ."

#. cHkur
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id7588732\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In an embedded chart data table, the data series are always organized in columns."
msgstr "ໃນຕາຕະລາງຂໍ້ມູນແຜນພູມທີ່ຝັງໄວ້, ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກຈັດລຽງເປັນຖັນສະເໝີ."

#. 5UCTC
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id95828\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For a new stock chart first use a column chart. Add the columns you need and enter your data in the order which is shown in the example, omitting any columns not required for the desired variant. Use <emph>Move Series Right</emph> to change the column order. Close the chart data table. Now use the <emph>Chart Type</emph> dialog to change to the stock chart variant."
msgstr "ສຳລັບແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນໃໝ່ ໃຫ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍແຜນພູມແທ່ງຕັ້ງກ່ອນ. ເພີ່ມຖັນທີ່ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງການ ແລະ ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຕາມລຳດັບທີ່ສະແດງໃນຕົວຢ່າງ, ໂດຍຂ້າມຖັນທີ່ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນສຳລັບຮູບແບບທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ໃຊ້ <emph>ຍ້າຍຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນໄປທາງຂວາ</emph> ເພື່ອປ່ຽນລຳດັບຖັນ. ປິດຕາຕະລາງຂໍ້ມູນແຜນພູມ. ຈາກນັ້ນໃຊ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ປະເພດແຜນພູມ</emph> ເພື່ອປ່ຽນເປັນຮູບແບບແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນ."

#. Brram
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id6182744\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you have already got a stock chart and you want to change the variant, then first change the chart type to a column chart, add or remove columns so that it fits to the variant, and then change the chart type back to a stock chart."
msgstr "ຫາກເຈົ້າມີແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນຢູ່ແລ້ວ ແລະ ຕ້ອງການປ່ຽນຮູບແບບ, ໃຫ້ປ່ຽນປະເພດແຜນພູມເປັນແຜນພູມແທ່ງຕັ້ງກ່ອນ, ເພີ່ມ ຫຼື ລຶບຖັນເພື່ອໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຮູບແບບນັ້ນ, ແລ້ວຈຶ່ງປ່ຽນປະເພດແຜນພູມກັບເປັນແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນຄືເກົ່າ."

#. uEiVg
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id3496200\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Do not write the name of a data series in a row. Write the name into the field above the role name."
msgstr "ຢ່າຂຽນຊື່ຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນໃນແຖວ. ໃຫ້ຂຽນຊື່ໃສ່ໃນຊ່ອງທີ່ຢູ່ເໜືອຊື່ບົດບາດ (role name)."

#. wnEUB
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id7599108\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The order of the rows determines how the categories are arranged in the chart. Use Move Row Down to change the order."
msgstr "ລຳດັບຂອງແຖວຈະກຳນົດການຈັດລຽງປະເພດຕ່າງໆໃນແຜນພູມ. ໃຊ້ ຍ້າຍແຖວລົງ ເພື່ອປ່ຽນລຳດັບ."

#. dtJha
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"hd_id888698\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Charts based on Calc or Writer tables"
msgstr "ແຜນພູມທີ່ອີງຕາມຕາຕະລາງ Calc ຫຼື Writer"

#. BaCXB
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id3394573\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can choose or alter a data range on the second page of the <emph>Chart Wizard</emph> or in the <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_data_range.xhp\"><emph>Data Range</emph></link> dialog. For fine tuning use the <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_data_series.xhp\"><emph>Data Series</emph></link> dialog."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້ໃນໜ້າທີສອງຂອງ <emph>ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</emph> ຫຼື ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_data_range.xhp\"><emph>ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph></link>. ສຳລັບການປັບແຕ່ງລະອຽດ ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_data_series.xhp\"><emph>ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ</emph></link>."

#. 8EpDr
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id7594225\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To specify a data range do one of the following:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອລະບຸຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ ໃຫ້ເຮັດຢ່າງໃດຢ່າງໜຶ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#. QHEUU
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id5081637\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the data range in the text box."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນໃນກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. xWcvR
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id9759514\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Calc, an example data range would be \"$Sheet1.$B$3:$B$14\". Note that a data range may consist of more than one region in a spreadsheet, e.g. \"$Sheet1.A1:A5;$Sheet1.D1:D5\" is also a valid data range. In Writer, an example data range would be \"Table1.A1:E4\"."
msgstr "ໃນ Calc, ຕົວຢ່າງຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນອາດຈະເປັນ \"$Sheet1.$B$3:$B$14\". ໃຫ້ສັງເກດວ່າຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນອາດຈະປະກອບດ້ວຍຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງພື້ນທີ່ໃນສະເປຣດຊີດ, ເຊັ່ນ \"$Sheet1.A1:A5;$Sheet1.D1:D5\" ກໍເປັນຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໃນ Writer, ຕົວຢ່າງຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນອາດຈະເປັນ \"Table1.A1:E4\"."

#. K4Qan
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id1614429\n"
"help.text"
msgid "As long as the syntax is not correct, %PRODUCTNAME shows the text in red."
msgstr "ຫາກໄວຍາກອນບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ, %PRODUCTNAME ຈະສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມເປັນສີແດງ."

#. 7CV3W
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id1589098\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Calc, click <emph>Select data range</emph> to minimize the dialog, then drag to select the data range. When you release the mouse, the data are entered. Click <emph>Select data range</emph> again to add a data range. In the input field of the minimized dialog, click after the entry and type a semicolon. Then drag to select the next range."
msgstr "ໃນ Calc, ຄລິກ <emph>ເລືອກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ເພື່ອຫຍໍ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມລົງ, ຈາກນັ້ນລາກເມົ້າເພື່ອເລືອກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ. ເມື່ອວາງເມົ້າ, ຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກປ້ອນເຂົ້າ. ຄລິກ <emph>ເລືອກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ອີກຄັ້ງເພື່ອເພີ່ມຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນອື່ນ. ໃນຊ່ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຂອງປ່ອງຢ້ຽມທີ່ຫຍໍ້ລົງ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ຫຼັງລາຍການແລ້ວພິມເຄື່ອງໝາຍຈ້ຳຈຸດ (;), ຈາກນັ້ນລາກເພື່ອເລືອກຊ່ວງຖັດໄປ."

#. b6qus
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id8746910\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click one of the options for data series in rows or in columns."
msgstr "ຄລິກເລືອກຕົວເລືອກໃດໜຶ່ງສຳລັບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນໃນແຖວ ຫຼື ໃນຖັນ."

#. t9ayj
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id9636524\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Your stock chart data are \"in columns\", if the information in a row belongs to the same \"candle stick\"."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນ \"ໃນຄໍລຳ\", ຖ້າຂໍ້ມູນໃນແຖວໃດໜຶ່ງຂຶ້ນກັບ \"ແທ່ງທຽນ\" ດຽວກັນ."

#. E7Zd4
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"hd_id5675527\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Fine Tuning the Data Ranges of Table Based Stock Charts"
msgstr "ການປັບແຕ່ງຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນແບບຕາຕະລາງໃຫ້ລະອຽດ"

#. ECYmF
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id3486434\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can organize data series and edit the source for parts of single data series on the third page of the <emph>Chart Wizard</emph> or on the page <emph>Data Series</emph> in the <emph>Data Range</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດລະບຽບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນສຳລັບບາງສ່ວນຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນດ່ຽວໄດ້ໃນໜ້າທີສາມຂອງ <emph>ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</emph> ຫຼື ໃນໜ້າ <emph>ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ຢູ່ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>."

#. zSfXf
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"hd_id3068636\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Organize Data Series"
msgstr "ຈັດລະບຽບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. kZMCC
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id2480849\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>data series</emph> area on the left side of the dialog, you can organize the data series of the actual chart. A stock chart has at least one data series containing the prices. It might have a second data series for transaction volume."
msgstr "ໃນສ່ວນ <emph>ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ທາງເບື້ອງຊ້າຍຂອງກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດລະບຽບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນຂອງແຜນພູມປັດຈຸບັນໄດ້. ແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນຈະມີຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ບັນຈຸລາຄາ. ມັນອາດຈະມີຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທີສອງສຳລັບປະລິມານການຊື້ຂາຍ."

#. FAXxK
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id4181951\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you have got more than one price data series, use the Up and Down arrow buttons to order them. The order determines the arrangement in the chart. Do the same for volume data series. You cannot switch price and volume data series."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານມີຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນລາຄາຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງຊຸດ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລູກສອນ ຂຶ້ນ ແລະ ລົງ ເພື່ອຈັດລໍາດັບພວກມັນ. ລໍາດັບດັ່ງກ່າວຈະກໍານົດການຈັດວາງໃນແຜນພູມ. ໃຫ້ເຮັດແບບດຽວກັນສຳລັບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນປະລິມານ. ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນລາຄາ ແລະ ປະລິມານໄດ້."

#. TL7Ud
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id2927335\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To remove a data series, select the data series in the list and click <emph>Remove</emph>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອລຶບຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນໃນລາຍການແລ້ວກົດ <emph>ລຶບອອກ</emph>."

#. E3oGt
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id2107303\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To add a data series, select one of the existing data series and click <emph>Add</emph>. You get an empty entry below the selected one, which has the same type. If you have no price data series or no volume data series, you must first select a range for these series in the <emph>Data Range</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວກົດ <emph>ເພີ່ມ</emph>. ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ລາຍການຫວ່າງເປົ່າຢູ່ລຸ່ມລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກ ເຊິ່ງມີປະເພດດຽວກັນ. ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ມີຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນລາຄາ ຫຼື ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນປະລິມານ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງເລືອກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນສຳລັບຊຸດເຫຼົ່ານີ້ກ່ອນໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>."

#. e9oGh
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"hd_id4071779\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Setting Data Ranges"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. VysRB
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id7844477\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Data Ranges</emph> dialog you can set or change the data range of each component of the selected data series."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນແປງຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງແຕ່ລະອົງປະກອບຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເລືອກໄດ້."

#. LCgsy
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id6478469\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the upper list you see the role name of the components and the current values. When you have selected a role, you can change the value in the text box below the list. The label shows the selected role."
msgstr "ໃນລາຍການທາງເທິງ ທ່ານຈະເຫັນຊື່ບົດບາດຂອງອົງປະກອບ ແລະ ຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນ. ເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກບົດບາດໃດໜຶ່ງແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນຄ່າໃນຊ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມລຸ່ມລາຍການໄດ້. ປ້າຍຊື່ຈະສະແດງບົດບາດທີ່ຖືກເລືອກ."

#. 6GFGB
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id9038972\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the range into the text box or click on <emph>Select data range</emph> to minimize the dialog and select the range with the mouse."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນໃສ່ໃນຊ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ກົດທີ່ <emph>ເລືອກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ເພື່ອຫຍໍ້ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບລົງ ແລະ ເລືອກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນດ້ວຍເມົາສ໌."

#. VhjWG
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id7985168\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select Open Values, Close Values, High Values, and Low Values in any order. Specify only the ranges for those roles which you need for the chosen variant of the stock chart. The ranges need not be next to each other in the table."
msgstr "ເລືອກ ຄ່າເປີດ, ຄ່າປິດ, ຄ່າສູງສຸດ, ແລະ ຄ່າຕໍ່າສຸດ ໃນລໍາດັບໃດກໍໄດ້. ລະບຸສະເພາະຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນສຳລັບບົດບາດທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ໃນຮູບແບບແຜນພູມຮຸ້ນທີ່ເລືອກ. ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຢູ່ຕິດກັນໃນຕາຕະລາງ."

#. MNrXk
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"hd_id876186\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Legend"
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກ"

#. PzXfx
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id3939634\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The legend displays the labels from the first row or column or from the special range that you have set in the <emph>Data Series</emph> dialog. If your chart does not contain labels, the legend displays text like \"Row 1, Row 2, ...\", or \"Column A, Column B, ...\" according to the row number or column letter of the chart data."
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກຈະສະແດງປ້າຍຊື່ຈາກແຖວ ຫຼື ຄໍລຳທຳອິດ ຫຼື ຈາກຊ່ວງພິເສດທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>. ຖ້າແຜນພູມຂອງທ່ານບໍ່ມີປ້າຍຊື່, ຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກຈະສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມເຊັ່ນ \"ແຖວ 1, ແຖວ 2, ...\", ຫຼື \"ຄໍລຳ A, ຄໍລຳ B, ...\" ຕາມໝາຍເລກແຖວ ຫຼື ຕົວອັກສອນຄໍລຳຂອງຂໍ້ມູນແຜນພູມ."

#. iBNcw
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id2377697\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The legend shows the value from the range, which you entered in the <emph>Range for Name</emph> field in the <emph>Data Range</emph> dialog. The default entry is the column header of the closing price column."
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກຈະສະແດງຄ່າຈາກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ປ້ອນໃສ່ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຊ່ວງສຳລັບຊື່</emph> ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນຫົວຂໍ້ຄໍລຳຂອງຄໍລຳລາຄາປິດ."

#. ENNoh
#: type_stock.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_stock.xhp\n"
"par_id2188787\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select one of the position options. When the chart is finished, you can specify other positions using the Format menu."
msgstr "ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກຕຳແໜ່ງໃດໜຶ່ງ. ເມື່ອສ້າງແຜນພູມສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດລະບຸຕຳແໜ່ງອື່ນໆໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ເມນູ ຮູບແບບ."

#. fA3NL
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Chart Type XY"
msgstr "ປະເພດແຜນພູມ XY"

#. SDqzE
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"bm_id84231\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>scatter charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>XY charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>chart types;XY (scatter)</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>error indicators in charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>error bars in charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>averages in charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>statistics in charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>variances in charts</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>standard deviation in charts</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ແຜນພູມແບບກະຈາຍ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ແຜນພູມ XY</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ປະເພດແຜນພູມ;XY (ກະຈາຍ)</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວຊີ້ບອກຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນແຜນພູມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ແຖບຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນແຜນພູມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍໃນແຜນພູມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ສະຖິຕິໃນແຜນພູມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄ່າຜັນປ່ຽນໃນແຜນພູມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ສ່ວນບ່ຽງເບນມາດຕະຖານໃນແຜນພູມ</bookmark_value>"

#. QBDn7
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"hd_id9346598\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"type_xy\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/type_xy.xhp\">Chart Type XY (Scatter)</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"type_xy\"><link href=\"text/schart/01/type_xy.xhp\">ປະເພດແຜນພູມ XY (ກະຈາຍ)</link></variable>"

#. RGBbY
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id2003845\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the first page of the <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">Chart Wizard</link> you can choose a chart type."
msgstr "ໃນໜ້າທຳອິດຂອງ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</link> ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກປະເພດແຜນພູມໄດ້."

#. SdHA4
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id791747395583502\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Then choose <emph>XY (Scatter)</emph>."
msgstr "ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກ <emph>XY (ກະຈາຍ)</emph>."

#. EHrHp
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"hd_id7757194\n"
"help.text"
msgid "XY (Scatter)"
msgstr "XY (ກະຈາຍ)"

#. DjFVF
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id5977965\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An XY chart in its basic form is based on one data series consisting of a name, a list of x‑values, and a list of y‑values. Each value pair (x|y) is shown as a point in a coordinate system. The name of the data series is associated with the y‑values and shown in the legend."
msgstr "ແຜນພູມ XY ໃນຮູບແບບພື້ນຖານແມ່ນອີງໃສ່ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນດຽວທີ່ປະກອບດ້ວຍຊື່, ລາຍການຄ່າ x, ແລະ ລາຍການຄ່າ y. ແຕ່ລະຄູ່ຄ່າ (x|y) ຈະຖືກສະແດງເປັນຈຸດໃນລະບົບເສັ້ນເຄົ້າ. ຊື່ຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນຈະເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຄ່າ y ແລະ ສະແດງຢູ່ໃນຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກ."

#. t9mUL
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id4381847\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose an XY chart for the following example tasks:"
msgstr "ເລືອກແຜນພູມ XY ສຳລັບຕົວຢ່າງວຽກງານດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#. 96vL4
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id1336710\n"
"help.text"
msgid "scale the x‑axis"
msgstr "ກຳນົດມາດຕາສ່ວນແກນ x"

#. 6oAUk
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id1221655\n"
"help.text"
msgid "generate a parameter curve, for example a spiral"
msgstr "ສ້າງເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງພາຣາມິເຕີ, ຕົວຢ່າງ ຮູບກົ້ນຫອຍ"

#. 4g38h
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id3397320\n"
"help.text"
msgid "draw the graph of a function"
msgstr "ແຕ້ມກຣາຟຂອງຟັງຊັນ"

#. 38iBq
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id7657399\n"
"help.text"
msgid "explore the statistical association of quantitative variables"
msgstr "ສຳຫຼວດຄວາມສຳພັນທາງສະຖິຕິຂອງຕົວປ່ຽນເຊີງປະລິມານ"

#. UXuBi
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id8925138\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Your XY chart may have more than one data series."
msgstr "ແຜນພູມ XY ຂອງທ່ານອາດຈະມີຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. kmPSk
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"hd_id5461897\n"
"help.text"
msgid "XY Chart Variants"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບຕ່າງໆຂອງແຜນພູມ XY"

#. Z8jEn
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id8919339\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can choose an XY chart variant on the first page of the <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">Chart Wizard</link>, or by choosing <item type=\"menuitem\">Format - Chart Type </item>for a chart in edit mode."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຮູບແບບແຜນພູມ XY ໄດ້ໃນໜ້າທຳອິດຂອງ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</link>, ຫຼື ໂດຍການເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຮູບແບບ - ປະເພດແຜນພູມ</item> ສຳລັບແຜນພູມທີ່ຢູ່ໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ."

#. azkUx
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id4634235\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The chart is created with default settings. After the chart is finished, you can edit its properties to change the appearance. Line styles and icons can be changed on the <emph>Line</emph> tab page of the data series properties dialog."
msgstr "ແຜນພູມຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ. ຫຼັງຈາກແຜນພູມສ້າງສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງມັນເພື່ອປ່ຽນຮູບລັກສະນະໄດ້. ຮູບແບບເສັ້ນ ແລະ ໄອຄອນສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ໃນແຖບ <emph>ເສັ້ນ</emph> ຂອງກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບຄຸນສົມບັດຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. 6AcaE
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id5482039\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Double-click any data point to open the <item type=\"menuitem\">Data Series</item> dialog. In this dialog, you can change many properties of the data series."
msgstr "ດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ຈຸດຂໍ້ມູນໃດໜຶ່ງເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ</item>. ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້, ທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງຄຸນສົມບັດຫຼາຍຢ່າງຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້."

#. vTuqs
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id0805200810492449\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For 2D charts, you can choose <item type=\"menuitem\">Insert - Y Error Bars</item> to enable the display of error bars."
msgstr "ສຳລັບແຜນພູມ 2 ມິຕິ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ແຊກ - ແຖບຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ Y</item> ເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ການສະແດງຜົນຂອງແຖບຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#. DEosY
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id6221198\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can enable the display of mean value lines and trend lines using commands on the Insert menu."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເປີດໃຊ້ການສະແດງຜົນຂອງເສັ້ນຄ່າສະເລ່ຍ ແລະ ເສັ້ນແນວໂນ້ມໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງໃນເມນູ ແຊກ."

#. rPRNq
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"hd_id1393475\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Points only"
msgstr "ສະເພາະຈຸດ"

#. JWLhZ
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id6571550\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Each data point is shown by an icon. %PRODUCTNAME uses default icons with different forms and colors for each data series. The default colors are set in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><item type=\"menuitem\">%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</item></caseinline><defaultinline><item type=\"menuitem\">Tools - Options</item></defaultinline></switchinline><item type=\"menuitem\"> - Charts - Default Colors</item>."
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະຈຸດຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກສະແດງດ້ວຍໄອຄອນ. %PRODUCTNAME ໃຊ້ໄອຄອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ມີຮູບຮ່າງ ແລະ ສີທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນສຳລັບແຕ່ລະຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ. ສີເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຖືກຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><item type=\"menuitem\">%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</item></caseinline><defaultinline><item type=\"menuitem\">ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</item></defaultinline></switchinline><item type=\"menuitem\"> - ແຜນພູມ - ສີເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ</item>."

#. CPMz6
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id331747339706540\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"chart2/res/valueaxisdirectpoints_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id71747339706542\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id61747339706545\">Icon Points only</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"chart2/res/valueaxisdirectpoints_52x60.svg\" id=\"img_id71747339706542\" width=\"0.6252in\" height=\"0.5417in\"><alt id=\"alt_id61747339706545\">ໄອຄອນ ສະເພາະຈຸດ</alt></image>"

#. kQvww
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id91747339706549\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Points only"
msgstr "ສະເພາະຈຸດ"

#. esJ88
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"hd_id5376140\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Lines Only"
msgstr "ສະເພາະເສັ້ນ"

#. VejUt
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id4408093\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This variant draws straight lines from one data point to the next. The data points are not shown by icons."
msgstr "ຮູບແບບນີ້ຈະແຕ້ມເສັ້ນຊື່ຈາກຈຸດຂໍ້ມູນໜຶ່ງໄປຫາຈຸດຖັດໄປ. ຈຸດຂໍ້ມູນຈະບໍ່ຖືກສະແດງດ້ວຍໄອຄອນ."

#. SG9fd
#: type_xy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id7261268\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The drawing order is the same as the order in the data series. Mark <emph>Sort by X Values</emph> to draw the lines in the order of the x values. This sorting applies only to the chart, not to the data in the table."
msgstr "ລໍາດັບການແຕ້ມແມ່ນຄືກັນກັບລໍາດັບໃນຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ. ໝາຍເອົາ <emph>ຈັດລຽງຕາມຄ່າ X</emph> ເພື່ອແຕ້ມເສັ້ນຕາມລໍາດັບຂອງຄ່າ x. ການຈັດລຽງນີ້ມີຜົນສະເພາະກັບແຜນພູມເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ບໍ່ມີຜົນກັບຂໍ້ມູນໃນຕາຕະລາງ."

