msgctxt ""
"type_xy.xhp\n"
"par_id7957396\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Smooth</emph> from the <emph>Line type</emph> dropdown to draw curves instead of straight line segments."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ໂຄ້ງມົນ</emph> ຈາກລາຍການ <emph>ປະເພດເສັ້ນ</emph> ເພື່ອແຕ້ມເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງແທນເສັ້ນຊື່."

