"par_id2507400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Positions the legend to the top of the chart.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ວາງຕຳແໜ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍສັນຍະລັກໄວ້ທາງເທິງຂອງແຜນພູມ.</ahelp>"

#. NKDKU
